information: As a family company, agaSAAT has stood for guaranteed top-quality baking, sprouting and spice seeds for over 25 years. With our extensive range, available in both organic and conventional quality, we supply wholesale trade and discerning bakers all over Germany, as well as private and industrial customers. Over the years, our customer network has grown to be as diverse as the products we offer. We supply customers in the spice processing and further processing industry, health food shops, homeopathic remedy manufacturers and other clients who use sprouting seeds in their work. Thanks to decades of experience in the international seed and spice trade, we are able to supply you with the highest-grade products from our headquarters in Neukirchen-Vluyn in the region of North Rhine-Westphalia. From growing your own plants to direct import, from laboratory testing to cleaning, germ reduction, mixing and packaging, you can rest assured that we have the right solution for your unique requirements.
